<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[السَّرْعَفَةُ]</span>: حُسن الغذاء،<span class="c5"> يقال:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>سرعفت الصبيَّ سرعفة وسرْعافاً <span class="c2">«٣»</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
